                            <comment id="14710675" author="gopalv" created="Tue, 25 Aug 2015 06:18:11 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ashutoshc&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ashutoshc&quot;&gt;ashutoshc&lt;/a&gt;: I kept the shim to allow -Phadoop-1 builds.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
